---
title: Tangy Steak & Bell Pepper Lo Mein with Tomato & Red Onion
description: Put down the takeout menu—this noodle stir-fry is ready in minutes! Thinly sliced steak is seasoned and seared in a flash, then tomato, bell pepper, red onion, and scallion cook to crisp-tender perfection. It’s all tossed with springy lo mein noodles in an umami-packed soy and Sriracha-infused sauce, then showered with fresh scallion greens.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663a46fdbe3ee05a950c3544-64e45b10.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/663a46fdbe3ee05a950c3544-en-US.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tangy-steak-and-bell-pepper-lo-mein-663a46fdbe3ee05a950c3544
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: East Asia
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 690 kcal
  fat: 22 g
